query:
SELECT id
        FROM (
            SELECT DISTINCT ON (m.id)
                m.id,
                m.queued
            FROM mods m

            -- exclude projects in tech review queue
            LEFT JOIN delphi_issue_details_with_statuses didws
                ON didws.project_id = m.id AND didws.status = 'pending'

            WHERE
                m.status = $1
                AND didws.status IS NULL

            GROUP BY m.id
        ) t

        ORDER BY queued ASC
        OFFSET $3
        LIMIT $2
